BIP-380 (Output Script Descriptors, General Operation), shipped
at
.IR share/doc/bitcoin/standards/bip-0380.mediawiki .
.IP \(bu 2
BIP-381 (Non-segwit output script descriptors), shipped at
.IR share/doc/bitcoin/standards/bip-0381.mediawiki .
.IP \(bu 2
BIP-386 (tr() output script descriptors), shipped at
.IR share/doc/bitcoin/standards/bip-0386.mediawiki .

.SH SEE ALSO
