.BR bitcoin-bip13 (1),
.BR bitcoin-bip32 (1),
.BR bitcoin-bip173 (1),
.BR bitcoin-descriptor (1),
.BR bitcoin-wallet (1)

.SH HISTORY
Plugin introduced in bitcoin 1.23.0 (FEAT-035 Stream B), extracted
from
.B bin/bitcoin
where the BIP-380 logic had landed in 1.4.0 (FEAT-009) and 1.18.0
(FEAT-026). The legacy
.B bitcoin descriptor checksum
/
.B verify
/
.B derive
verbs continue to work as deprecated aliases until 1.24.0.
.B bitcoin descriptor wallet
is not deprecated \(em it stays in
.BR bitcoin (1)
as a wallet-touching helper.
